snippet.title: Tiny Atolls Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
TINY ATOLLS is a minimalist building strategy game Build bridges across colorful islands, unlock new tiles and complete quests to expand your world!
Wishlist Tiny Atolls here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2246640/Tiny_Atolls/
